45:38.003 --> 45:42.507
* I'm thinking what if,
what if it's romance and *

45:42.573 --> 45:46.477
* It's got me wondering
how does this song end? *

45:46.544 --> 45:50.916
* I'm thinking what if,
what if, what if *

45:50.982 --> 45:54.920
* What if I told him
